cast.overview: Recently fired and desperate for work, a troubled young man named Mike agrees to take a position as a night security guard at an abandoned theme restaurant: Freddy Fazbear's Pizzeria. But he soon discovers that nothing at Freddy's is what it seems.
cast.title: Five Nights at Freddy's

details.biography: Cory DeVante Williams, more commonly known as "CoryxKenshin"  is a popular YouTuber and internet personality known for his gaming content. He gained fame through his energetic and comedic commentary while playing various video games, particularly horror and action games. CoryxKenshin has a dedicated fan base and is well-regarded for his positive attitude and entertaining videos.
details.name: Cory Kenshin
